{"type": "article", "id": 9727, "title": "MONO 3D 打印个性化眼镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-19T07:18:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235708LXGEp4Dko6MvVbPl.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t香港建筑师 Edmond Wong 认为眼镜应该像衣服一样，找到精确的尺码才能保证佩戴的舒适。于是他设计了一款叫做 “MONO” 的眼镜，试图通过 3D 打印技术打印出最合适使用者的尺寸，从而提升眼镜佩戴的舒适程度。他们的镜框尺寸系统由三部分组成，分别是镜框的宽度、鼻托的宽度以及眼镜臂的长度，通过三项数据的组合，找到最合适的尺寸。同时，这种镜框的制作一气呵成，没有螺丝等连接物，也不需要零件的组装。且材料上比市面上普通的板料镜框轻一半。<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/mono-an-eyewear-3d-printed-to-fit-your-face\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235704Pq8Ki3mvsXdZBNzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523570587xwFGUjXPQk3l5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235705iXwYrHPIlOJu069F.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235705MwNyntYdiobC1e2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65729167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235706ibThF3Q8jBZYyevl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235706a5Mheotq3IGXLWb9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235707dCwlJp2jLSV7BWzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64791667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235707iUP8FezDuq1dWAG5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.47604167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/upload